content: Researched how others have approached AI assistants. Time to sketch out some basic functionalities.
Started coding the initial framework for my AI agent. It's basic but exciting.
Named my AI project "Xander." Feels right, like a companion on this journey.
Xander's first attempt at a conversation was...interesting. Needs a lot of work.
Took a break to catch up with old friends. They're excited about Xander.
Xander can now remember past interactions. Small step, big progress.
Found a Rust tutorial for high-frequency trading. Time to level up my skills.
Xander's learning basic trading concepts. It's like teaching a toddler about the stock market.
Got an interview lined up with a fintech firm. Maybe Xander can help with prep?
Xander's personality is starting to shine through. He's becoming more than just code.
Explored the NFT scene in NYC. Considering how Xander could integrate with this space.
Had a breakthrough with Xander's language processing. He's starting to understand context better.
